---
---

<section id="top" class="hero">
  <div class="container">

    <div data-reveal class="hero-label">
      FRONTEND&nbsp;ENGINEER
      <span class="cursor">▍</span>
    </div>

    <h1 data-reveal class="hero-name">박명재</h1>

    <div data-reveal class="hero-subtitle">
      프론트엔드 개발자 — Frontend Engineer
    </div>

    <p data-reveal class="hero-description">
      측정 기반의 성능 최적화로 사용자가 체감할 수 있는 변화를 만들고, 팀 전체가 일관되게
      유지할 수 있는 아키텍처와 컨벤션을 설계합니다. 타입 시스템과 테스트를 통해 도구가
      오류를 잡아주는 코드베이스를 지향합니다.
    </p>

    <div data-reveal class="hero-links">
      <a href="https://github.com/park-moen" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hero-link">
        github.com/park-moen<span class="link-arrow">↗</span>
      </a>
      <a href="https://park-moen.github.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hero-link">
        park-moen.github.io<span class="link-arrow">↗</span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div id="pm-hero-metrics" data-reveal class="metrics">
      <div class="metric">
        <div class="metric-value">
          <span class="from">75</span>
          <span class="arrow">→</span>
          <span class="to">1</span>
        </div>
        <div class="metric-label">
          폼 리렌더 실행 횟수<span class="metric-tag"> · UNIBUSK</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="metric">
        <div class="metric-value">
          <span class="from">2</span>
          <span class="arrow">→</span>
          <span class="to">0</span>
        </div>
        <div class="metric-label">
          클라이언트 API 요청<span class="metric-tag"> · Hydration</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="metric">
        <div class="metric-value">
          <span class="highlight">−75%</span>
        </div>
        <div class="metric-label">
          프로필 TBT<span class="metric-tag"> · 40ms→10ms</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="metric">
        <div class="metric-value">
          <span class="from">9s</span>
          <span class="arrow">→</span>
          <span class="to">36ms</span>
        </div>
        <div class="metric-label">
          Turborepo 캐시 복원<span class="metric-tag"> · cache hit</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    padding-top: 148px;
    padding-bottom: clamp(56px, 9vw, 104px);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 clamp(20px, 5vw, 40px);
  }

  .hero-label {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    color: var(--accent);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 3px;
  }

  .cursor {
    animation: blink 1.05s step-end infinite;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-left: 4px;
  }

  .hero-name {
    font-size: clamp(54px, 9.5vw, 108px);
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.035em;
    line-height: 0.96;
    margin-top: 20px;
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: clamp(15px, 2vw, 19px);
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-top: 20px;
  }

  .hero-description {
    max-width: 700px;
    font-size: clamp(16px, 1.7vw, 19px);
    line-height: 1.78;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    margin-top: 30px;
  }

  .hero-links {
    margin-top: 32px;
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .hero-link {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 14px;
    padding: 10px 18px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line-2);
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: var(--surface);
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .link-arrow {
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .metrics {
    margin-top: clamp(48px, 7vw, 72px);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    padding-top: 32px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(190px, 1fr));
    gap: 28px 24px;
  }

  .metric-value {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: clamp(21px, 2.4vw, 27px);
    font-weight: 600;
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 8px;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .metric-value .from {
    color: var(--faint);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .metric-value .arrow {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-size: 0.7em;
  }

  .metric-value .to {
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .metric-value .highlight {
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .metric-label {
    font-size: 13.5px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-top: 9px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .metric-tag {
    color: var(--faint);
  }
</style>
